N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 3.4 - Native lizards

State Regulations
(a) Definitions. For purposes of this section, native lizards shall mean all life
stages, including eggs, of the following species: northern fence lizard, five-lined skink, and northern coal skink. (b) Open season. None. Notes
